Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Urban Light at LACMA
Description: A very nice spot, very luminous and fun to take pictures at night in LA and get awesome results.

Name: Balboa Park
Description: A big park to walk around for the day,relax, it has cute buildings, photogenic spots,  have fun, and enjoy nature!

Name: Solvang
Description: A small town, to just spend the day walking around , eating pasties and ice cream with family or friends, great way to take a break and discover new places.

Name: Catalina Island
Description: A very amazing place for a weekend getaway, go camping, get distracted, it has a very pretty and relaxing beach, it has a lot of nature, hiking trails and just a lot of activities.

Name: Cancun
Description: A city with summer vibes, it has a lot of flora and fauna, it is very touristy place,has a pretty beach and many activities and places to have a lot of fun with friends and family.
